
1. to build message anaylzer c++ library:

  $ cd cxx
  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake ..
  $ make
  $ cd ../../

2. to make the RulesEngine class available to Python:

  $ ln -s cxx/build/ErrorHandler/RE.so RE.so

3. run the tests for LogicEngine.py

  Only once, you have to install pytest. If we get pytest installed
  directly on the machine, then we don't have to do this bit:
  $ pip install --user pytest

  $ PYTHONPATH=$PWD pytest
